rComments: didn't do well in Scott's 255 class even though Nate was the TA. Did extremely well in his class though, I guess his essay format lecture played a big role

Took this class as an elective and it was nothing like I expected but in a good way! The prof is really nice and funny and makes the material very clear. He makes use of technology (youtube, memes, etc.) and so the lectures are really interesting. Do the readings before you go to class and you will do well. Also he looks just like Dallas Green!

while attendence is not mandatory I found it very helpful to do the readings once then go to his lecture because he summarizes all the main points in the article in lecture. I noticed that his lecture notes are in an "essay" format and that's how he lecture. He tend to speak fast when he's reading off his notes so you might benefit from recording.

He was the TA for my class in sexual diversity studies.  Responded super fast to emails and was willing to meet to talk about my assignments/tests and give really great feedback.  I think he TA's for UNI255 too cause my friend said she had him as well.
